BucBattle:
1. Must display the current score.
2. Must have 3 ship types, but can have more.
3. Must be able to play in web browser.
4. Must be compatible with IOS and Android.
5. Ships must sink when their health reaches less than or equal to 0.
6. PLayer's ship must be ETSU themed.
7. Smaller shipss must shoot projectiles faster.
8. Smaller ships' projectiles must deal less damage.
9. Bigger ships must shoot projectiles slower.
10. Bigger ships' projectiles must deal more damage.
11. More ships/enemies must be added for each level completed.
12. Left and right arrow buttons must control movement, but could be implemented to follow finger horizontal position.
